{"tid":588554,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[公投]中醫算唔算係偽科學？","createTime":"2018-03-11T09:42:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-12T01:52:17.000Z","uid":86587,"like":18,"dislike":25,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"b8a53fc15ba087376db6943be161168f80284166","tid":588554,"uid":86587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T09:42:07.000Z","msg":"前幾日見到有個post話中醫廢到連末期癌症都發現唔到。有感而發，中醫其實係咪好多concept，eg熱氣, 腎虧, 血氣都無一個準確科學定義<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 真係嘅話啲中醫真係可以亂鳩咁嚟害死人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n大家點睇？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係偽科學<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔係偽科學"},{"pid":"1a033456c7f6e7aae5ce8aa186f625618d77ba7a","tid":588554,"uid":57418,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T15:39:22.000Z","msg":"套得入現代科學檢測方法個part 唔係，未套或套唔到個d可以當係偽科學甚至宗教，但都有佢存在價值例如安慰效應都可以醫人"},{"pid":"4a6b5e48fd7144dad787ec373b49c6c6fa1417bf","tid":588554,"uid":57418,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"1a033456c7f6e7aae5ce8aa186f625618d77ba7a","tid":588554,"uid":57418,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T15:39:22.000Z","msg":"套得入現代科學檢測方法個part 唔係，未套或套唔到個d可以當係偽科學甚至宗教，但都有佢存在價值例如安慰效應都可以醫人"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T15:42:01.000Z","msg":"安慰劑效應"},{"pid":"2b3e84ae4c3bf3bce3f82203f1a5981e91b1f922","tid":588554,"uid":158270,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T16:10:14.000Z","msg":"唔可以話有效就係科學，冇效就係偽科學。<br />\n係科學定偽科學，要睇佢有冇得證偽。<br />\n我認為中醫嘅陰陽五行論係偽科學，但臨床實驗總結嘅經驗部分，如穴位針灸就係科學。"},{"pid":"754702e7aa47ae7fdd9df37d492da4a0938fbad8","tid":588554,"uid":22302,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T20:30:22.000Z","msg":"應該叫<span style=\"color: red;\">非</span>科學<br />\n但如果有人將佢包裝做科學，咁就變成偽科學"},{"pid":"b7bed8ce349f60e0f77e66d22b54e58b3955b269","tid":588554,"uid":22302,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"754702e7aa47ae7fdd9df37d492da4a0938fbad8","tid":588554,"uid":22302,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T20:30:22.000Z","msg":"應該叫<span style=\"color: red;\">非</span>科學<br />\n但如果有人將佢包裝做科學，咁就變成偽科學"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T20:31:02.000Z","msg":"好似通常真正中醫師唔會話中醫係科學<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔太肯定"},{"pid":"8d25d74887eb79b8169bf7c6730cd26c4bafcf3a","tid":588554,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b8a53fc15ba087376db6943be161168f80284166","tid":588554,"uid":86587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T09:42:07.000Z","msg":"前幾日見到有個post話中醫廢到連末期癌症都發現唔到。有感而發，中醫其實係咪好多concept，eg熱氣, 腎虧, 血氣都無一個準確科學定義<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 真係嘅話啲中醫真係可以亂鳩咁嚟害死人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n大家點睇？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係偽科學<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔係偽科學"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T01:40:26.000Z","msg":"中醫：細菌發現前醫學<br />\n西醫：細菌發現後醫學<br />\n<br />\n目前定位：中醫係另類治療、替代醫學"},{"pid":"ba147bb3fd4346cde9553167918c688ff9624873","tid":588554,"uid":171520,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T01:52:17.000Z","msg":"中醫係一套唔完整既科學，草藥運用，針灸療法，同樣係靠前人既經驗累積而得出成效，只係經絡和氣既概念比較抽象，所以俾人覺得係神化"}]}